high_descs: Turn to the right and walk forward to the toilet. Make a left at the toilet and face the bin.
Take the sponge out of the bin.
Turn around and walk to the bath tub. Make a right and walk to the sink.
Put the sponge in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water.
Pick up the sponge and turn to the right and go forward to the shelf on the wall.
Place the sponge on the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Wet a sponge and put it away on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn right, head to the trash can past the toilet.
Pick up the sponge in the trash can.
Turn around, bring the sponge to the sink on the right.
Wash the sponge in the sink with water.
Bring the sponge to the shelf on the right
Put the sponge on the bottom shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put a cleaned sponge on a shelf.

high_descs: Turn right and walk ahead to the black container on the floor against the wall.
Pick up the green sponge from inside the container.
Turn around, hang a right at the tub and walk to the sink.
Put the sponge in the sink, rinse it a few seconds and pick it back up.
Turn right and walk to the white shelves ahead against the wall.
Put the rinsed sponge on the bottom shelf to the left of the gold roll.
anns.task_desc: Place a rinsed sponge on a shelf.
